section.div: Project Leader of @OWASP Amass and VP of Attack Surface Protection at @zerofox-oss
Reaching this goal will allow even more of my time to be focused on open-source security tool development.

div.p: Hi! I develop (usually in Go) information security tools. Specifically, I am the founder and project leader for the OWASP Amass Project that performs attack surface mapping and asset discovery.
